.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, police-officer, firefighter, project-manager
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing, rugby, rowing, tennis
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, marigold, sunflower, balloon-flower
5 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, snooker, bridge, billiard
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, mystery, romance, epic, thriller

1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the designer
2. the person who's sport is surfing is the person watching family movies
3. the person playing monopoly is the dressmaker
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person playing canasta
5. the dressmaker is to the right of the police-officer
6. the person who growspoppy is the person watching thriller movies
7. the person who growslily is the firefighter
8. the person playing snooker is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies
11. the person who growslily is to the left or right of the person watching epic movies
12. the person who growssunflower is the person playing bridge
13. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who growsballoon-flower
14. the person who's sport is rowing is to the left or right of the project-manager

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Sport	|   rowing	|    rugby	|     ice-hockey	|    surfing	|    tennis	|
| Job		|    firefighter	|      project-manager	|      designer	|     police-officer	|     dressmaker	|
| Game	|     billiard	|      canasta	|      snooker	| bridge	|     monopoly	|
| Flower		|     lily	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| sunflower	|   parliament	|
| Movie-Genre		|     mystery	|     epic	|     thriller	|     family	|     romance	|
